## 📊 Dashboards

### Import Pre-built Dashboards

In Grafana → **Dashboards → Import**:

| Dashboard | Grafana ID |
|---|---|
| Node Exporter Full | `1860` |
| Windows Exporter | `14694` |

### Dashboard Variable Fix

If panels show **"No data"**, check the `JOB` variable at the top of the dashboard matches your Prometheus job names:

| Exporter | Job name in `prometheus.yml` |
|---|---|
| Node Exporter | `node_exporter` |
| Windows Exporter | `windows_exporter` |

